N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1152.5 - Right-of-way

State Regulations

All vehicles shall yield the right-of-way to any and all
aircraft in motion, except emergency equipment which shall have tower clearance
when responding to an alarm. Notes
